@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@json = application/json
@savedCharacterId = 1

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}} HTTP/1.1
Accept: {{json}}

###

### Registrar usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/register HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}

{
  "name": "Joao Fischer",
  "email": "joao@exemplo.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

###

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}

{
  "email": "joao@exemplo.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

###

### Usuário autenticado atual
GET {{baseUrl}}/me HTTP/1.1
Accept: {{json}}

###

### Listar personagens salvos do usuário logado
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters HTTP/1.1
Accept: {{json}}

###

### Salvar personagem
POST {{baseUrl}}/characters HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}

{
  "name": "Rick Sanchez",
  "species": "Human",
  "image": "https://rickandmortyapi.com/api/character/avatar/1.jpeg",
  "url": "https://rickandmortyapi.com/api/character/1"
}

###

### Buscar personagem salvo por id
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters/{{savedCharacterId}} HTTP/1.1
Accept: {{json}}

###

### Atualizar personagem salvo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/characters/{{savedCharacterId}} HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}

{
  "name": "Rick Sanchez Editado",
  "species": "Human",
  "image": "https://rickandmortyapi.com/api/character/avatar/1.jpeg",
  "url": "https://rickandmortyapi.com/api/character/1"
}

###

### Excluir personagem salvo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/characters/{{savedCharacterId}} HTTP/1.1
Accept: {{json}}

###

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout HTTP/1.1
Accept: {{json}}

###

### Verificar sessão após logout
GET {{baseUrl}}/me HTTP/1.1
Accept: {{json}}
